## How to run it

1. Open `stock_analysis.ipynb` in [Google Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/)
2. Run all cells (Runtime → Run all)
3. Data is pulled live from Yahoo Finance via `yfinance`, so results update automatically each time it's run

## Built with

- Python
- pandas
- yfinance
- matplotlib

